            <div class="title">
                Clause 1â€”(Substitution Of Eighteen Months As Term Of Whole-Time Service)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-12-06/debates/b27f167f-26c5-4414-8eec-4221c846080a/ControlOfEngagementOrder" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
