        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-10f6dc6e-e9b2-4d87-88ca-fa9f73c2f282">
                Dr. Haden Guest  (Islington, North)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-10f6dc6e-e9b2-4d87-88ca-fa9f73c2f282" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-12-06/debates/2cc32de8-2a74-4641-8b89-9021619ac0ba/Clause1%E2%80%94(SubstitutionOfEighteenMonthsAsTermOfWhole-TimeService)#contribution-10f6dc6e-e9b2-4d87-88ca-fa9f73c2f282">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Will the hon. and learned Gentleman explain what he means by "under-the-counter medical deferment?"</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-10f6dc6e-e9b2-4d87-88ca-fa9f73c2f282" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
