<p class="">My hon. Friend is doing it very well, and I thank him very much.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c5633e03-7d66-4b8f-a612-4af6ff009892" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
