                The Chairman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-73f3f69e-a819-430c-8e06-5434386452b7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-12-06/debates/2cc32de8-2a74-4641-8b89-9021619ac0ba/Clause1%E2%80%94(SubstitutionOfEighteenMonthsAsTermOfWhole-TimeService)#contribution-73f3f69e-a819-430c-8e06-5434386452b7">
