                Mr. S. Silverman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-24fb2d6c-b0e8-4513-acf5-45fe19356ec4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
