van, Rt. Hon. A. (Ebbw Vale)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Collins, V. J</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fletcher, E. G. M. (Islington, E)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Binns, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Colman, Miss G. M</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Foot, M. M.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Blackburn, A. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Corlett, Dr. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gibbins, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Blenkinsop, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Crawley, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gibson, C. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Boardman, H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Crossman, R H S</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Glanville, J. E.(Consett)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bottomley, A. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Daggar, G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Greenwood, A. W. J (Heywood)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bowden, Flg. Offr. H. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Daines, P</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Grey, C. F</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division"> </table></p><p class="Division"></division></p>
