<p class="">if hon. Members want an assurance, I give them this guarantee, that we shall use every endeavour, in cooperation with the authorities on the spot and with the voluntary organisations, to safeguard the moral well-being of our boys.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
