<p class="">May I ask one question in order to complete the picture of the responsibility of the Secretary of State? Will he tell us why it was found necessary that this deputation should visit Germany, and why it was necessary that the Archbishop of Canterbury and other dignitaries should make statements?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
