                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b6034e9e-a55d-4d8a-8460-d734b379e220" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
