        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-8f1c547c-80fe-4a83-a2fd-561bd57addf5'>
            
<p class="">repeat once more, on behalf of the Government, that we shall use every possible means of improving the moral condition of our men overseas.</p>
