we, C.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>McFarlane, C. S.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Walker-Smith, D.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dugdale, Maj. Sir T. (Richmond)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mackeson, Brig. H. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wheatley, Colonel M. J (Dorset, E.)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Eccles, D. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Maclean, F. H. R (Lancaster)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, Sir D. (Fareham)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Eden, Rt. Hon. A</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Maitland, Comdr. J. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>White, J. B. (Canterbury)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Foster, J. G. (Northwich)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Manningham-Butler, R. E</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Willoughby de Eresby, Lord</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Fraser, Sir I. (Lonsdale)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Marlowe, A. A. H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gates, Maj. E. E</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Marshall, D. (Bodmin)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></p><p class="Division">  <b>TELLERS FOR THE NOES</b></p><p class="Division"> </td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mr. Byers and Mr. Wadsworth</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division"> </table></p><p class="Division"></division></p>
