                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ff78253a-8196-4c63-bf7f-a9d32e816cc6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-12-06/debates/2cc32de8-2a74-4641-8b89-9021619ac0ba/Clause1%E2%80%94(SubstitutionOfEighteenMonthsAsTermOfWhole-TimeService)#contribution-ff78253a-8196-4c63-bf7f-a9d32e816cc6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
